《'''虚幻游戏'''》（{{lang-en|Mazes and Monsters}}）是一部1982年的美国[[電視電影|電視電影]]，由{{tsl|en|Steven Hilliard Stern|史蒂文·希利亚德·斯特恩|}}执导，讲述的是一群大学生对一个同名的[[角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]（RPG）产生了浓厚的兴趣。<ref name=NYT>{{cite web|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1982/12/28/arts/tv-mazes-and-monsters-fantasy.html|title=TV: 'MAZES AND MONSTERS,' FANTASY|author=O'Connor, John J.|date=1982-12-28|access-date=2018-05-21|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119045729/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/12/28/arts/tv-mazes-and-monsters-fantasy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

26岁的[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]在这部电影中首次领衔主演。<ref name="Wired">{{cite news |last=Kushner |first=David |title=Dungeon Master: The Life and Legacy of Gary Gygax |work=Wired.com |url=http://archive.wired.com/gaming/virtualworlds/news/2008/03/ff_gygax?currentPage=all |accessdate=2008-10-16 |date=2008-03-10 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031210259/http://archive.wired.com/gaming/virtualworlds/news/2008/03/ff_gygax?currentPage=all |archivedate=2014-10-31 }}</ref>

